description: Ten people are injured and a further 10 are still unaccounted for in Gjerdrum, authorities say.
title: Norway landslide: Houses buried in Gjerdrum village near Oslo
title_page: Norway landslide: Houses buried in Gjerdrum village near Oslo - BBC News
maintext: More than 30 homes have been destroyed, but officials say more could be lost as the edges of the crater left by the landslide are still breaking away. Officials have warned people to stay away from the area.
